  "message": "fix(web): move MIME type fix to root vercel.json\n\nThe packages/web/vercel.json was causing Vercel to build from the wrong\ndirectory, breaking monorepo workspace dependencies. Move the .ts MIME\ntype fix to the root vercel.json which properly handles the monorepo.\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
